WEBVTT

00:01:59.624 --> 00:02:02.378
"When we keep on saying this,
nothing is going to change.

00:02:02.402 --> 00:02:03.775
We are in charge here.

00:02:03.799 --> 00:02:06.295
We should do something about this,

00:02:06.319 --> 00:02:09.683
so that we do want
to have our parents here."

00:02:10.773 --> 00:02:13.781
We talked about that,
and what we saw every day

00:02:13.805 --> 00:02:17.498
was that the people
that lived in our nursing home

00:02:17.522 --> 00:02:19.887
were confused about their environment,

00:02:19.911 --> 00:02:23.458
because what they saw
was a hospital-like environment,

00:02:23.482 --> 00:02:27.593
with doctors and nurses
and paramedics in uniform,

00:02:27.617 --> 00:02:29.284
and they lived on a ward.